        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: 'I was the one who ordered the decorations to be taken down—Wanshi, the sleepyhead, kept hitting them when he woke up. It wasn\\'t a big deal for Constructs, sure...', 4: '2'}"
