        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'You\\'re mistaken. Wanshi would use that as an excuse to avoid practice, so I spent some effort replacing all the decorations, and I put all these paddings on the edges and corners of the tables and chairs.', 4: '2'}"
